title: Cyril Dubroca
text:
Cyril Dubroca (born February 8, 1981 in <a href="Mont-de-Marsan">Mont-de-Marsan</a>) is a French professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. Currently, he plays in the <a href="Championnat%20de%20France%20amateur">Championnat de France amateur</a> for <a href="Gen%C3%AAts%20Anglet">Genêts Anglet</a>.
He played on the professional level in <a href="Ligue%201">Ligue 1</a> for <a href="Toulouse%20FC">Toulouse FC</a>.
